<P>&sect; XLII. The officers who compo&s;ed this tribunal were
&s;o &s;en&s;ible of the law's &s;everity, that they unanimou&s;ly &s;ub|&s;cribed
a letter to the board of Admiralty, containing this
<PB N="68" REF="70">
remakable paragraph:&mdash;&startq;We cannot help laying the
