and in order to make good the &s;um which had been i&s;&s;ued
<PB N="211" REF="215">
by his Maje&s;ty's orders, in pur&s;uance of the addre&s;s from
the Commons, they now allotted four millions, twenty-two
thou&s;and, eight hundred and &s;even pounds, &s;even
&s;hillings, and three-pence. They unanimou&s;ly granted,
as a pre&s;ent &s;upply in the then critical exigency, towards
